    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ninja Fights 是一款 2D 垂直卷轴冒险游戏，你将成为一名熟练的忍者。穿越复杂的关卡，解决挑战性的谜题并发现隐藏的宝藏，利用隐身和手里剑克服障碍和敌人。在这款充满动作的游戏中掌握你的忍者技能！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553800/extras/5e71fea6881e70578e5e5929744742a2.poster.avif?t=1756483052\" width=610 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553800/extras/5e71fea6881e70578e5e5929744742a2.webm?t=1756483052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553800/extras/5e71fea6881e70578e5e5929744742a2.mp4?t=1756483052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于 Ninja Fights</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ninja Fights 邀请你沉浸在一场激动人心的 2D 垂直卷轴冒险中。扮演一名忍者大师，穿越 40 个独特设计的关卡，面对强烈的挑战。每个关卡都充满了复杂的谜题和致命的陷阱，需要技巧和策略才能克服。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553800/extras/c32692ca922023841120edd43852d38e.poster.avif?t=1756483052\" width=610 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553800/extras/c32692ca922023841120edd43852d38e.webm?t=1756483052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553800/extras/c32692ca922023841120edd43852d38e.mp4?t=1756483052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >参与史诗级的首领战，考验你的能力和反应，每一场战斗都带来独特的挑战。利用你的忍者技能，如隐身、敏捷和手里剑，穿越危险的环境，避免陷阱，智胜敌人。随着游戏进展，发现隐藏的宝藏和秘密，增加冒险的深度和可重玩性。</p>",
